spec_data.Name: perl-Package-DeprecationManager
spec_data.Description:
This module allows you to manage a set of deprecations for one or more modules.

When you import Package::DeprecationManager, you must provide a set of
-deprecations as a hash ref. The keys are "feature" names, and the values are
the version when that feature was deprecated.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:50:46 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Manage deprecation warnings for your distribution
